---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Privacy Policy | Project 51 - Data Protection & User Rights"
    description="Read Project 51's comprehensive privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data. GDPR compliant with clear information on cookies, third-party services, and your privacy rights."
>
    <div class="bg-slate-900 min-h-screen">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div
            class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 py-16 md:py-20"
        >
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-liberation-blue/10 border border-liberation-blue/30 mb-6"
                >
                    <span class="text-2xl">üîí</span>
                    <span
                        class="text-sm font-mono text-liberation-blue tracking-wider uppercase"
                        >Privacy Policy</span
                    >
                </div>
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4 leading-tight"
                >
                    Privacy <span
                        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-liberation-blue to-cyan-400"
                        >Policy</span
                    >
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-2">
                    How we collect, use, and protect your information
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 font-mono">
                    Last Updated: January 13, 2026
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 pb-20">
            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
                <!-- Introduction -->
                <div
                    class="bg-slate-800/30 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8"
                >
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-0 mb-4">
                        Introduction
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-0">
                        Project 51 ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to
                        protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains
                        how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your
                        information when you visit our website. Please read this
                        privacy policy carefully.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Information We Collect -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        1. Information We Collect
                    </h2>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                        1.1 Automatically Collected Information
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        When you visit our website, we automatically collect
                        certain information about your device, including:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        <li>IP address</li>
                        <li>Browser type and version</li>
                        <li>Operating system</li>
                        <li>Referring URLs</li>
                        <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
                        <li>Geographic location (country/region level)</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                        1.2 Voting and Interaction Data
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        When you participate in our referendum or use our
                        services:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        <li>Vote choices (Yes/No)</li>
                        <li>Hashed IP address (to prevent duplicate votes)</li>
                        <li>Timestamp of interactions</li>
                        <li>Country code of origin</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                        1.3 User-Generated Content
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        Information you voluntarily provide when using our
                        tools:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        <li>
                            ID Generator: Names, dates, photos (stored locally)
                        </li>
                        <li>Asset Calculator: Financial data (not stored)</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <!-- How We Use Information -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        2. How We Use Your Information
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        We use the information we collect to:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        <li>Operate and maintain our website</li>
                        <li>Display referendum results and statistics</li>
                        <li>Prevent fraudulent voting</li>
                        <li>
                            Analyze website usage and improve user experience
                        </li>
                        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
                        <li>
                            Display relevant advertisements (Google AdSense)
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <!-- Cookies and Tracking -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to:
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                        3.1 Essential Cookies
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        <li>Session management</li>
                        <li>Vote tracking (prevent duplicates)</li>
                        <li>User preferences</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                        3.2 Analytics Cookies
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        We may use Google Analytics or similar services to
                        understand how visitors use our site.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                        3.3 Advertising Cookies
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        Google AdSense uses cookies to serve ads based on your
                        prior visits to our website or other websites. You can
                        opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a
                            href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads"
                            class="text-liberation-blue hover:underline"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Settings</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Third-Party Services -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        4. Third-Party Services
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        We use the following third-party services:
                    </p>

                    <div
                        class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4"
                    >
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                            Google AdSense
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-2">
                            We use Google AdSense to display advertisements.
                            Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your
                            visits to this site and other sites.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads"
                            class="text-liberation-blue text-sm hover:underline"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            >Google's Advertising Privacy Policy</a
                        >
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4"
                    >
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">
                            Cloudflare
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-2">
                            Our website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages.
                            Cloudflare may collect certain technical
                            information.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/"
                            class="text-liberation-blue text-sm hover:underline"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            >Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Data Security -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        5. Data Security
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        We implement appropriate technical and organizational
                        security measures to protect your personal information.
                        However, no method of transmission over the Internet is
                        100% secure.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
                        <li>IP address hashing for vote tracking</li>
                        <li>Local-only storage for ID Generator data</li>
                        <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <!-- Your Rights -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        6. Your Privacy Rights
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        Depending on your location, you may have the following
                        rights:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal
                            data
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate
                            data
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your data
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Opt-out:</strong> Opt out of personalized advertising
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Data Portability:</strong> Request transfer of
                            your data
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-slate-300">
                        To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a
                            href="mailto:contact@notrealgreenland.com"
                            class="text-liberation-blue hover:underline"
                            >contact@notrealgreenland.com</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Children's Privacy -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        7. Children's Privacy
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        Our website is not intended for children under 13 years
                        of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information
                        from children under 13. If you believe we have collected
                        information from a child under 13, please contact us
                        immediately.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Changes to Policy -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We
                        will notify you of any changes by posting the new
                        Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last
                        Updated" date.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Contact -->
                <section class="mb-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        9. Contact Us
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please
                        contact us:
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4"
                    >
                        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-2">
                            <strong>Email:</strong>
                            <a
                                href="mailto:contact@notrealgreenland.com"
                                class="text-liberation-blue hover:underline ml-2"
                                >contact@notrealgreenland.com</a
                            >
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-0">
                            <strong>Website:</strong>
                            <a
                                href="/"
                                class="text-liberation-blue hover:underline ml-2"
                                >Project 51</a
                            >
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Disclaimer -->
                <div
                    class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 mt-12"
                >
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-red-400 mb-3">
                        ‚ö†Ô∏è Satirical Content Disclaimer
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm mb-0">
                        This website is a satirical project and thought
                        experiment. While we take your privacy seriously and
                        comply with all applicable laws, the content and
                        "referendum" are fictional and for entertainment
                        purposes only.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
